# Git Rules

- always add [AI Agent] at the front of the commit message if you doing commit
- always update the changelog file before doing any commit; if there is no changelog file, create one
- always include the date and time in the changelog and use tags at the front of each items, e.g.: [Add],[Update],[Remove]
- always update the changelog tags definition section when you created a new tag and with the explaination